ENABLE / DISABLE
  Start or stop automatic game updates.  (Deity only.)

SYNTAX
  enable
  disable
  enab
  disa

DESCRIPTION
  'enable'  - allows the update loop to run on its normal schedule.
  'disable' - pauses the update loop.  No production, no population
              change, no distribution.  The server keeps running but
              time is frozen from a game perspective.

  Only the deity can use these commands.
  Useful when making major world changes or importing/exporting data.

  Current update state is shown in the 'update' command output.

EXAMPLE
  disable                   pause the game clock
  enable                    resume normal updates

SEE ALSO
  update  shutdown  force  add
